Ba6 18. Bxa6 Rxa6 19. Raf1 Rb6 20. Qh6 Qf8 21. Qh4 Rb4 22. a3 Rc4 23. Nd2 Rd4
24. Nb3 Rdxe4 25. Nxe4 Rxe4 26. Rf4 Rxf4 27. Qxf4 Nxd5 28. Qf3 N5b6 29. Nd2 Ne5
30. Qe4 f5 31. Qb7 Nbd7 32. Qd5+ Kg7 33. Nc4 Nxc4 34. Qxc4 Ne5 35. Qd5 Qb8 36.
b3 c4 37. bxc4 Qa7+ 38. c5 Nf7 39. Kh1 dxc5 40. Qb3 c4 41. Qc3+ Kg8 42. Re1 Qa4
43. Qf6 Qd7 44. Rb1 Qc7 45. Re1 Qd7 46. Rb1 Qc7 47. Qc3 Nd6 48. Rc1 Qc6 49. Qd4
h6 50. Qf6 Kh7 51. Rd1 c3 52. Rxd6 {A combined 6th place in Rapid and 4th
place in Blitz propelled the South African only GM to a third place in the
